data.description: This charming 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home is situated on a spacious corner lot in the desirable Valley Gardens neighborhood. The living room boasts large windows and a vaulted ceiling, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. Throughout the home, you'll find natural colors and attractive wood-look floors, providing a warm and welcoming feel. The kitchen is a highlight with its bright white decor, abundant cabinets, granite countertops, and a stylish tile backsplash. It's a functional space that combines both aesthetics and practicality. A dedicated laundry room with an extra closet for storage adds convenience to your daily routine. Notably, the laundry room also serves as a mudroom, with a door leading to the backyard for easy access. The home includes two well-proportioned bedrooms as well as 1.5 baths, ensuring convenience for both residents and guests. Step outside onto the covered deck, where you can enjoy views of the expansive yard with beautiful mature trees. This outdoor space provides a perfect setting for gatherings or quiet moments in nature. Additionally, the oversized 2.5 car garage provides ample room to comfortably park two full-sized vehicles side by side, ensuring convenient access and maneuverability as well as extra storage. Overall, this property offers a delightful combination of comfort, style, and outdoor appeal in a welcoming neighborhood. Call today!
